Package com.googlecode.mobilityrpc.protocol.protobuf Description

[private api] This package contains machine-generated Google Protocol Buffer (protobuf) classes for encoding messages to/from binary.

Classes in this package are auto-generated by Protobuf's protoc compiler in the Maven compile phase of the build. They will be saved into this package, but in the target/generated-sources/ directory.

For documentation on protocol messages and how they are processed, see each of the .proto files in src/main/proto.
